Greetings, Insti Junta!

Today, the Music Club brings to you what is undoubtedly one of its most fun
events: *Drum Circle*! This event is for anybody who has always wanted to
try their hands at percussion, and for those who haven't, this event has
something for you too!

So, enthu people, come on down to *Himalaya* at*6 P.M. today* and bring you
friends along so  nobody misses out on having a good time!

IITM Music Club

P.S. No drumming fundaes required; like we said, this event is for
everybody.

P.P.S Do bring Odomos to protect yourself from mosquitoes.



